reviewText: This 3 tape series, of which this is the 3rd, is Excellent - which is even inadequate to describe the set.  Why, oh why, haven't these been put on DVD???

I would have given this ( stars but it was only on s VHS tape. I had to have it copied onto a cd disc at great expense.  It is a lovely tape to watch however!!! It was all worth the added expense etc.
